name: Dynamic Active Global Equity Income ETF
longDescription: To achieve its objectives, DXGE will invest primarily in a wide range of equity securities from around the globe which includes dividend or distribution paying equity securities and real estate investment trusts, as well as in other types of equity securities. DXGE seeks to provide income and longterm capital appreciation.
